# Lints after work

- **After** a coherent task or meaningful source edit: run workspace diagnostics on changed paths and fix issues you introduced (includes `tentura_lints` plugin rules via `dart analyze` / `flutter analyze`).
- **Before** `git commit` (or staging a commit): re-check the same scope so analyzer/CI stays green.

## `tentura_lints` (`packages/tentura_lints`)

Rules live under `packages/tentura_lints/lib/src/rules/`; register in `lib/main.dart`. Enabled for the workspace via root `analysis_options.yaml` `plugins:` (not per-package `custom_lint:`). CI runs `dart analyze --no-fatal-warnings` (server) and `flutter analyze --no-fatal-warnings --no-fatal-infos` (client), which include plugin diagnostics (see `.github/workflows/pipeline.yml`). Full wording: **Static enforcement** in `architecture.mdc`.

| Rule | One line |
|------|----------|
| `no_domain_to_data_or_ui_import` | Client `lib/domain/`: no `package:tentura/.../data/` or `.../ui/` imports. |
| `no_cubit_to_data_service_import` | Client `**/ui/bloc/*_cubit.dart`: no `.../data/service/` imports. |
| `no_map_dynamic_in_use_case_api` | `**/lib/domain/use_case/**/*.dart`: public API must not return `Map<String, dynamic>` / `List<Map<…>>` / bare `dynamic`. |
| `no_raw_graphql_in_dart` | No inline GraphQL document strings or `gql('…')`; use `.graphql` + generated `*Req`. |
| `no_inline_font_size` | Client `lib/features/**` + `lib/ui/**`: no numeric literal `TextStyle(fontSize: …)` (use `TextTheme` / `TenturaText`; allow-list `design_system/`, `rating_scatter_view.dart`, `colors_drawer.dart`). |
| `cubit_requires_use_case_for_multi_repos` | Client `packages/client/.../ui/bloc/*_cubit.dart`: ≥2 repo params ⇒ must inject a `*Case`. |

**Baselines:** existing debt uses `// TODO(contract): Phase-2 DTO migration — …` plus `// ignore: tentura_lints/<rule>` until Phase 2 DTO work removes them.
